Name: Pure Dark Tide Frequency
AttributesDescription: A pure reverberation from the Dark Tide of the past.
BgDescription:
Pure and silent, this frequency has slumbered long enough to leave no ripples. As the firstborn of the Dark Tide, it carries the ancient will of its mother. Undeniably powerful yet defiant, it betrayed its creator in the abyss and now sleeps alone in the dark realm.
Only the sweet Resonance can stir its dreamless sleepâ€¦ and awaken its long-forgotten hunger.
ObtainedShowDescription: A pure reverberation from the Dark Tide of the past. Sending it back to the Back Shores could help the Tethys System pinpoint the False Sovereign's hideout.
